==== SOURCE

https://www.entrepreneur.com/article/325923

==== AGENT

Amazon product recommendation

==== GOAL

Recommend products the customer might be interested in

==== DATA

They collect data from everyone that uses their service. They collect information such when the customer buys a product, what customers with similar buying habits purchase and how customers rate their purchase.

==== METHODS

They used data from users to predict habits of customers.

==== RESULTS

Amazon can predict the products you want to buy by looking at customers with similar buying habits.

==== COMMENTS

Amazon recomendations has helped me find good deals on products that I was looking to buy.